Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Shugo Chara TV Shopping!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shugo Chara TV Shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everyone doing well-dechu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cute, convenient, and low, low prices...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's time for Shugo Chara TV Shopping-dechu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, the product we'll be introducing to you today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's great! Totally awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't even brought out the product yet-dechu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My bad... My timing was totally off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The product we'll be introducing to you today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's everyone's best friend, the little duckie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's a duck! Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take it down a notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, this little duckie isn't just good for decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can train those difficult to reach muscles by rocking it back and forth-dechu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! This rocking rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H–Hey, that's dangerous-dechu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to the next product, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The audience is waiting for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the next item we'll introduce is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tightrope-dechu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice! Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look what you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:19.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Get close to me and you'll get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't do that! I'm outta control!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, why so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheer up and move on to the next product!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next item we will introduce is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My heart is beating "hurry up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:39.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...we will introduce is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody can stop my beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great products!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice products!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Producers produce the products!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could the next product be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're having a blowout on annoying Rhythms-dechu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:04:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With every purchase you'll receive an annoying, high-strung Rhythm-dechu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Order now and receive a giggling Kusukusu as a gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not cool, that's {\i1}cold{\i0}, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Operators are on the line now!
