Dialogue: 4,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya Hikaru!
Dialogue: 4,0:05:04.48,0:05:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the President of Easter, Hikaru used to fight against the Guardians.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:10.00,0:05:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he's now transferred to Seiyo Academy as a first year student.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now he's friends with Amu-chan and the others!
Dialogue: 4,0:05:16.88,0:05:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being close to everyone is helping him learn human kindness and warmth.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:24.64,0:05:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll keep doing these Shugo Chara Encyclopedias each week!
Dialogue: 4,0:05:28.74,0:05:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look forward to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shugo-shugo Open Heart Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to do another personality test to find out the truth about yourself today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you watching at home, play along, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, the question:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would you like to go to a fancy restaurant with among these choices?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ikuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With Hikaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to choose, but with Tadase-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagihiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has everyone at home made up their minds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to announce the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What we'll find out today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much do you love yourself?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, for the people that chose Ikuto...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.43,0:06:33.67,TS Sign1,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(440,662)\q2\fs30\bord0.5\c&HE5552A&\3c&HE5552A&}You're always\Npositive
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.81,0:06:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really love yourself!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:27.79,0:06:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Clover, do you love yourself?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:33.67,0:06:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, for those of you that chose Tadase...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:36.72,0:06:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are disappointed in yourself a lot!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.12,0:06:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dia, do you lack self-confidence sometimes?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:42.58,0:06:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.80,0:06:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just because you're too hard on yourself.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have more self-confidence and you'll be okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:49.79,0:06:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:50.86,0:06:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, for those of you that chose Hikaru...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.86,0:06:59.73,TS Sign1,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(394,647)\q2\fs24\bord0.5\c&HE5552A&\3c&HE5552A&}Being praised\Nmakes you\Nhappy
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You both like and dislike yourself equally!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heart, is that right?
Dialogue: 2,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, for those of you that chose Nagihiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a secret narcissist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't show it in front of people because you're embarrassed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but deep down in your heart you think you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like, she poses in front of a mirror and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today we found out that Spade is a secret narcissist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.92,Dialogue Alt,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not! It's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, don't say yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about for everyone at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until the next shugo-shugo open heart game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's wrong, it's wrong! Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.94,Dialogue Alt,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's wrong.
