Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:08:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should I really express these feelings of mine to Kiseki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love troubles?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If he says okay, then I'd have\Nto give up on Rhythm, wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wants it all, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lost, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try listening to what your heart is saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now matter how dark the night sky is spread out before you, there are always shining stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you gaze at the sparkling stars and focus your eyes, you should be able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be able to see the sparkle in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't understand at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just leave the interpreting to Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, and just confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't know which one to choose, then how about confessing to both of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dia wouldn't say something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'd say something more complicated–
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:58.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what if I'm turned down by both of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like dandelion fluff dancing on a gust of wind, you know not your own fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no matter what place you may end up, you can bloom into a wonderful flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll feel better once you get an answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you might find another love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The infinite possibilities within you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The expanding world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The you you do not know is surely there, somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself and just go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now me and Dia will give worrying Miki a cheer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go, go, Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can do it, you can do it, Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it, but I'm full of confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you! I'm gonna go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's it for Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and Dia's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Advice Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiseki, Rhythm!
