Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amu-chan, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd you run off all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sensed something amiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An X Egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I can't really place it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This girl doesn't have a heart's egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It became an X Egg and flew off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the X Egg broke her stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That heart's egg is this girl's would-be self.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her would-be self has flown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened to the X Egg that left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this rate it might become lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's search for her egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where could it have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, let me borrow this for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's search ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiseki, you watch over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed! You commoners leave this up to the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Rikka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you trying to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I just forgot something, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgot something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this where you live, Rikka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y–Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can sense X Eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T–T–That's just your i–i–imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my pets' fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your pets?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:14:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R–Right! I forgot to feed my pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got, like, catfish and tarantulas and crocodiles and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Catfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tarantula?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crocodile?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're tiny, Dia, so they might mistake you for their meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just wait right there, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why I feel this strange sensation like X Eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Attention please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoever recognizes this stuffed animal, speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess it's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,X Egg, come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't feel it anywhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wait... We'll find it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not here. Where could it have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,887)\q2}I wonder what it feels like to\Nput an X on your would-be self.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I don't really know who I want\Nto be, so I can't even imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your would-be self is somewhere inside you, Rikka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may not notice it, but it sleeps inside of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day you'll be able to notice that radiance, Rikka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside of me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,888)}I wonder who it is I want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rikka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can sense an X Egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's stealing everyone's willpower!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,429)}It seems different than the usual X Eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a strong feeling of sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't go doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you are that girl's X Egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and go back to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch out, Rikka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amu-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've told you again and again, it's dangerous by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Rikka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, is that her X Egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's more powerful than usual. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tadase-kun, take care of Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried, but I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,647)}Violin, calligraphy, piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to do them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(1395,2406,\c&HFFFBF5&\3c&HFFFBF5&\4c&HFFFBF5&)}...but I gave up easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,930)}And when my beloved Mii-chan's ear came off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I couldn't do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(1898,3817,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}And I gave up, yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate myself for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I give up on everything so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For someone like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For someone like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't give up! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You go for it, and go for it, and give it your all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\q2}And I'm sure you'll become\Nsomeone who doesn't give up easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to try so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what if you can't do it at first?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day when you're older, you might be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trying hard can tire you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to force it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,974)}Just go along at your own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And be that person you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Negative Heart: Lock On!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Open Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hatched into a Guardian Character!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm your would-be self.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Guardian Character Mii!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do my best, nice and slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Yuka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mii?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. I have the same name as your bunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down and go slowly... Slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could hear you when I was fixing Mii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I gave up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be together from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take our time and slowly, gradually, eventually turn into a girl who can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll always be together with you, Yuka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guardian Characters sure are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really rough to place an X on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to return every X Egg to its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even with an X on it, that doesn't change the fact that it's who you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,978)}Who I want to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder who I want to be.
